A Logical Volume Manager is needed on Unix servers, and so it is needed
also on Linux.
If this LVM is obsoleted, then when will LVM2 be merged?
really we cannot have a 2.6 or 3.0 tree without a Volume Manager, it would
be a big fault.
Luigi
